24 The Fragrance "Gold" is inspired by Jack Bauer from the TV series 24 (which is the longest running series in TV history and ranked as the 6th greatest television show of all-time!) The precious gold coloured bottle inspires feelings of power and success. With this scent you'll be able to embody Jack's extraordinary strength of character and determination through adversity - all without raising a sweat!

Product Details
The 24 Gold fragrance opens with vibrant
column21: dynamic tones and has a  captivating fresh
column23: oriental fragrance.    It contains notes of  jasmine
column25:
amber and vanilla.

Caution
Flammable
Keep away from sources of ignition
Keep away from children
Do not use near fire

flame or heat
Avoid spraying near the eyes
